content: Hi, I want to open a savings account
Hello! I'd be happy to help you with opening a savings account. BPI offers several savings account options with competitive interest rates and flexible terms.

suggestions.suggestion: Hello! I'd be happy to help you with opening a savings account. BPI offers several savings account options with competitive interest rates and flexible terms.

content: For our regular savings account, you'll need: 1) Valid ID, 2) Initial deposit of ₱500, 3) Filled application form. Would you like me to provide more details about our savings account features?

suggestions.suggestion: For our regular savings account, you'll need: 1) Valid ID, 2) Initial deposit of ₱500, 3) Filled application form. Would you like me to provide more details about our savings account features?

content: Our regular savings account offers 0.25% annual interest rate with daily interest computation. For higher interest rates, you might want to consider our BPI Maxi-Saver which offers up to 1.5% annually.

suggestions.suggestion: Our regular savings account offers 0.25% annual interest rate with daily interest computation. For higher interest rates, you might want to consider our BPI Maxi-Saver which offers up to 1.5% annually.

content: You can start your application online through BPI Online or visit any BPI branch. For online applications, you'll need to schedule an appointment for document verification.
